This is Service for Postmaster module [https://objectivehtml.com/index.php] which allows SMS notification to be sent.

It requires account with Twilio gateway [https://www.twilio.com]

To install, simply copy over the files. Now you should be able to select "SMS" as "Email Service" for all your Parcels, Hooks and Notifications in Postmaster Control Panel.

"From email" and "To email" fields should contain sender/recipient phone numbers in international format (numbers only prefixed with +, e.g. +1234567890). Other then this, set up SMS notifications just like you do with email notifications.

Postmaster module is required.